f=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/id/default/wp-plugins/woocommerce/\">(Plugin) WooCommerce</a>: 99%</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Contoh penerjemahan yang layak:</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-1 galeri-strings wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex\">\n\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2440\"  class=\"wp-image-2440\" src=\"https://wp-id.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/272659506_686252315920137_4381783793690081509_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2449\"  class=\"wp-image-2449\" src=\"https://wp-id.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/299845067_639454617333434_8352997673221791283_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2448\"  class=\"wp-image-2448\" src=\"https://wp-id.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/288773888_278905077752448_3854407038997928902_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2447\"  class=\"wp-image-2447\" src=\"https://wp-id.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/288578338_4976951025748747_5129494705074247249_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2446\"  class=\"wp-image-2446\" src=\"https://wp-id.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/288099199_765060158260736_940913937707949469_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2445\"  class=\"wp-image-2445\" src=\"https://wp-id.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/285196605_556050299292110_7786096586756741410_n.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-id=\"2444\"  class=\"wp-image-2444\" src=\"https://wp-id.or